Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.23,0:00:06.93,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不做廚師了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.93,0:00:09.68,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,如果在食戟上輸給你的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.08,0:00:12.28,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我就再也不身負「幸平」的招牌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.02,0:00:16.02,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,發誓不再出現在專業的廚房中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.86,0:00:19.57,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話與一百把廚具的價值相稱了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.66,0:00:23.13,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,順便節省你一個工序吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.77,0:00:26.53,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,第二輪比賽的題目是西餐的主食
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.15,0:00:28.39,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我會做這個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.64,0:00:30.24,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,牛肉…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.39,0:00:31.32,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.39,0:00:32.77,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你在透露些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.80,0:00:34.84,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不要把你要做的料理暴露出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.24,0:00:36.65,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,反正都會被預測出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.78,0:00:38.57,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,輸了的話再也不能當廚師了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.85,0:00:40.78,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,幸平 我看錯你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.88,0:00:44.59,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,對於你來說料理是那種隨手可棄的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.94,0:00:45.68,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,水戶同學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.70,0:00:46.77,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我不管你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.22,0:00:48.03,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,肉魅親
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.70,0:00:49.48,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,創真君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.44,0:00:52.00,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不當廚師了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.55,0:00:55.46,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,把塔克米君的半月刀奪回來就足夠…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.55,0:00:55.46,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\pos(936,1005)}mezza luna
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.46,0:00:56.50,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.79,0:01:00.28,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我要你把到現在搶過來的一百把廚具
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.42,0:01:02.46,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,物歸原主
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.82,0:01:05.35,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,賭上我作為廚師的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.59,0:01:06.77,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,也會將你打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.19,0:01:08.55,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,美作昴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.08,0:01:11.04,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,成立了 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.82,0:01:12.89,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,食戟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.03,0:01:37.54,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}比心中描繪的意象更遙遠的彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.13,0:01:43.97,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}在一筆筆敘寫  那真實還在遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.84,0:01:47.85,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}如無盡的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.97,0:01:52.89,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}來將各自的自尊心研磨透亮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.23,0:01:57.90,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}敞開任何言語之類的裝飾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.02,0:02:07.32,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}相互碰撞 相互摩擦 rolling stone
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.45,0:02:09.99,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}相遇是 shockwave shockwave
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.03,0:02:15.08,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}向未知的世界邁出腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.08,0:02:17.63,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}無謀的挑戰者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.63,0:02:22.96,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}只要用手中的刀劈開明天就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.01,0:02:25.05,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}這並不是別人的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.17,0:02:28.84,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}是只屬於自己的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.97,0:02:34.81,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}因為我們都是未經琢磨的鑽石！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.02,0:01:13.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,——————OP——————
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.03,0:01:37.54,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}思い描いてるイメージより遙か向こう側へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.13,0:01:43.97,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}創り上げて行く　真実はまだ遠く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.84,0:01:47.85,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}果てない旅路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.97,0:01:52.89,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}お互いのプライドを研ぎ澄ませよぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.23,0:01:57.90,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}言葉なんて飾りは開けさせりやいい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.02,0:02:07.32,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}ぶつかり合い　磨かれていく　rolling stone
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.45,0:02:09.99,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}出會いは　shockwave shockwave
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.03,0:02:15.08,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}まだ知らない世界へ歩き始めた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.08,0:02:17.63,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}無謀な挑戦者さ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.63,0:02:22.96,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}手にした刃で明日を切り開けばいいんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.01,0:02:25.05,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}誰かのもんじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.17,0:02:28.84,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}自分だけのストーリー
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.97,0:02:34.81,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}cause we are still rough diamonds on the road!
