Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.28,0:22:18.83,shokeki_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}堰きを切た喉から手がでるほど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.24,0:22:20.66,shokeki_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}欲しいぐなだんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.08,0:22:24.41,shokeki_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}僕じゃない　別の誰か
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.08,0:22:29.54,shokeki_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}夢と希望　他に何がいると
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.88,0:22:34.80,shokeki_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}思えだ頃の僕は今いつーごえ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.09,0:22:37.43,shokeki_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}長い物に巻がれで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.72,0:22:40.06,shokeki_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}失った道しるべ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.43,0:22:42.77,shokeki_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}生ど死の狭間にわ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.93,0:22:45.73,shokeki_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}スノードロップが咲き乱れる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.89,0:22:48.15,shokeki_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}何かの間違いで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.56,0:22:51.19,shokeki_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}砕け散ってしまったなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.36,0:22:56.32,shokeki_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}せめで僕の抜け殻に　花束を添えて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.57,0:23:01.74,shokeki_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}こんなもんかな　こんなもんでしょう　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.24,0:23:07.04,shokeki_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}あきらめだと思われたって構わないけど　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.25,0:23:12.75,shokeki_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}僕らしくない　僕らしくない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.09,0:23:17.38,shokeki_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}誰にだて作れもんに価値はない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.34,0:23:30.03,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你在這個星期
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.15,0:23:31.12,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,買過什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.51,0:23:32.60,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,遇到過誰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.06,0:23:34.74,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,嘗試過什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.28,0:23:37.15,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我都瞭若指掌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.40,0:23:39.24,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,美作也…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.86,0:23:41.38,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,牛尾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.04,0:23:44.68,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,香辛料是丁香和黑胡椒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.25,0:23:46.27,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,連Matignon也是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.02,0:23:47.84,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.19,0:23:48.94,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,相同的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.33,0:23:51.99,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,和幸平的料理過程完美同步了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.91,0:23:57.79,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那 就從這裡開始超越他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.76,0:24:00.77,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那個肉是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.82,0:24:02.76,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,改良
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.81,0:24:10.32,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 早晨依舊會來臨
